data-image-src="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/wp-content/themes/socius/images/bg-testimonials.jpg" data-natural-width="2000" data-natural-height="700"><div class="container"><div id="quote" class="col-xs-12">“</div><div id="review_container"><div id="reviews"><div class="reviews_content"><div class="review_comment">I just recently had my roof done by Zeke &amp; Son. I have to say that this was a very positive experience. Zeke brought in a SWAT team of workers who stripped and finished the roof in one full day.The&hellip;</div></div><div class="reviews_content"><div class="review_comment">Best ever!!! He came out on a Sunday!! He was very professional , polite, quick , clean and very helpful!! He even fixed a few thing that I did not know needed attention!”</div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 center"><a href="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/testimonials/" class="sq_btn">View All Testimonials</a></div></div><div class="parallax-overlay full"></div></div></div><div id="galleryBG" class="full"><div id="car"><div id="gallery_title" class="wrapper"><h2 class="center">Project Portfolio</h2><div class="triangle"></div></div><div id="carContainer"><div><a href="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/wp-content/gallery/footer-gallery/bigstock_Modern_House_3055318.JPG" id="image-13" rel="lightbox[1]"><img data-src="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/wp-content/gallery/footer-gallery/thumbs/thumbs_bigstock_Modern_House_3055318.JPG" alt="bigstock_Modern_House_3055318" /></a></div><div><a href="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/wp-content/gallery/footer-gallery/bigstock-Contemporary-Style-Home-2731424.jpg" id="image-16" rel="lightbox[1]"><img data-src="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/wp-content/gallery/footer-gallery/thumbs/thumbs_bigstock-Contemporary-Style-Home-2731424.jpg" alt="Contemporary Style Home" /></a></div><div><a href="https://zekeandsonroofing.com/wp-content/gallery/footer-gallery/bigstock-The-roof-of-the-house-with-nic-88686371.jpg" id="image-19" rel="lightbox[1]"><img data-src=